params.baseToken: should be the underlying mintable ETF security
params.priceFeeds: should all have the same denomination (I.E ETH/USD and BTC/USD)
params.tokens: is constructed array from priceFeeds. Always contains 1 less index than priceFeeds

returns.nav: returns the total price relative to the denominated asset and total baseToken supply
